           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      rf-cli-cod-cge       to   v-num                  .
