      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * S-e-p-a-r-a-t-o-r-i                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "NN"                 to   w-scr-str-tip          .
           perform   cmp-sng-fld-000      thru cmp-sng-fld-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Codice tipo operazione                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9"                  to   v-edm                  .
