           move      zero                 to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
       exe-exp-mgi-620.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
           if        w-exe-ctr-001        >    6
                     go to exe-exp-mgi-640.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
